description: 31 Mercer #2 is a BRAND NEW 2 Bed/2.5 Bath ideally located in South Boston's Telegraph Hill neighborhood. Unit has 942 sq ft of living area and large PRIVATE rear deck. Unit features hardwood floors throughout, recessed lighting, Central Air, in-unit laundry. Custom kitchen has 4+ seat island with white Caesarstone countertops, Alvic Luxe Modern Slab Cabinetry, Fisher/Paykel integrated appliances + vent hood. Primary Bedroom has en suite bath with floating double vanity, tiled floors, frameless glass shower + 2 closets with custom build outs. Additional bedroom, full bath + half bath. Open concept floor plan with plenty of space for relaxation + entertaining. Private deck off living area. Visual entry system allows remote access. 31 Mercer is a short walk to everything South Boston has to offer including area beaches, bars/restaurants on East + West Broadway, public transportation and highway access at I-93, I-90 + Express to Logan. Easy to show!
